data.description: Discover your dream home in Copperas Cove, Texas, with this exquisite 2020-built 5-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence, nestled on a sprawling 2.7-acre lot. This modern home combines luxury with the tranquility of country living. The interior boasts an open-plan design, bathed in natural light, featuring contemporary finishes and a show-stopping kitchen. Efficiency upgrades include Spray Foam insulation. Step outside to your own slice of paradise, where a serene wet weather creek at the rear of the property, enhancing its natural beauty. The land is perfect for animal enthusiasts, with a well-maintained livestock pen, and offers an RV parking space complete with electric hookups, catering to both adventure seekers and those who love to host. Located in a peaceful yet accessible part of Copperas Cove, this property provides the ideal balance of rural charm and city convenience, close to schools, shopping, and local amenities. This property is more than a home; it's a lifestyle opportunity for those seeking space, comfort, and a connection with nature. Schedule your viewing today and take the first step towards owning your piece of Texas heaven.
